# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback — serve the locale-correct app shell for
# client-side routes (/foundations/branding, …). Static assets (/bundle.js,
# /styles.css, /brand/*) and the prerendered pages are matched first; only
# unknown paths hit these rules. Locale-prefixed unknowns fall back to that
# locale's shell so the language survives a deep link.
/vi/*  /vi/index.html  200
/zh/*  /zh/index.html  200
/*     /index.html     200
